         <repository label="Repository:">Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library</repository>
         <abstract label="Abstract:">Videotapes of sessions from the symposium and published proceedings, "Future Directions in Electrical Engineering: Proceedings of the Cornell University Electrical Engineering Centennial Symposium series, March 15-June 12, 1985," edited by Simpson Linke. Topics discussed include technological innovations in electrical engineering and electronics, social aspects of electrical engineering, space sciences, and power resources.</abstract>
         <langmaterial label="Language:">Collection material in <language encodinganalog="041" langcode="eng">English</language>
         </langmaterial>
      </did>
      <scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520">
         <head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
         <p>Videotapes of sessions from the symposium and published proceedings, "Future Directions in Electrical Engineering: Proceedings of the Cornell University Electrical Engineering Centennial Symposium series, March 15-June 12, 1985," edited by Simpson Linke. Topics discussed include technological innovations in electrical engineering and electronics, social aspects of electrical engineering, space sciences, and power resources.</p>
      </scopecontent>
